title: 2007 Svenska Supercupen
text: Svenska Supercupen 2007, "Swedish Super Cup 2007", was a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> match played on 31 March 2007 between <a href="Allsvenskan%202006">Allsvenskan 2006</a> champions <a href="IF%20Elfsborg">IF Elfsborg</a> and <a href="Svenska%20Cupen">Svenska Cupen 2006</a> winners <a href="Helsingborgs%20IF">Helsingborgs IF</a>. This was the first edition of a super cup in Sweden. Elfsborg won the game 1-0 after a goal from <a href="James%20Keene%20%28footballer%29">James Keene</a> in the 55th minute. The attendance wasn't very positive for the new Swedish tournament, only 1,240 saw the match on <a href="Bor%C3%A5s%20Arena">Borås Arena</a>.
